@startuml web-client
title WorkflowDev — Web Client (fluxo unidirecional, sem framework)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

[app.js\n(bootstrap / listeners\n+ poll 10s)] as App
[state.js\n(state central + drafts\n+ sessionStorage)] as State
[handlers.js\n(router + eventos\n+ polling diff)] as Handlers
[mutations.js\n(valida + POST\n+ base64 anexos)] as Mut
[http.js\n(fetch JSON)] as Http
[view_model.js\n(deriva: filtra/agrupa\n+ validadores)] as VM
[view.js\n(board + new issue)] as View
[detail_view.js\n(detalhe da Issue)] as Detail
[markdown.js / gherkin.js] as Helpers

cloud "API HTTP\n/api/issues" as API

App --> Handlers : eventos delegados
Handlers --> State : lê/atualiza
Handlers --> Mut : ações de escrita
Handlers --> View : render board
Handlers --> Detail : render detalhe
Mut --> Http : POST
Http --> API
View --> VM
Detail --> VM
Detail --> Helpers
View --> State
Detail --> State

note bottom
  Fluxo: DOM event -> handlers -> mutations (API)
  -> muta state -> re-render (innerHTML completo).
  Polling re-renderiza só quando o JSON muda
  (preserva scroll/seleção e <details> expandidos).
end note
@enduml
